high_descs: Turn around and walk around to face the opposite side of the center table.
Pick up the knife on the center table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three slices.
Turn left and walk to the end of the counter to face the trash can.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Turn around and walk around the room to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up the piece of apple on the counter.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk to the end of the counter to face the trash can.
Place the apple piece in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat an apple piece plus place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward, turn left at the table where the wine bottle is, go to the table.
Take the knife behind the wine bottle from the table.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Cut the apple to the right of the sink into pieces.
Turn left, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward, turn right at the green bin to the left of the oven.
Put the knife in the bin.
Turn around, go forward to the table, turn left, go forward a step, turn right, go forward, turn left to the sink, go to the sink.
Take a piece of apple that was cut.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave. Take the apple from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward, turn right at the green bin to the left of the oven.
Put the apple in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a green bin.

high_descs: Turn around to move between the door and the end of the island, then head left and face the island just past the bench seat.
Pick up the knife from between the salt shaker and wine bottle.
Turn right and carry the knife to the kitchen sink.
Slice the apple on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left to move to the stove, then head left again to the green trash bin just past the stove.
Place the knife in the trash bin.
Turn right to move back to the kitchen sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter next to the sink.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Turn around to move towards the stove and then turn left to stand in front of the green trash bin next to the stove again.
Put the apple slice in the green trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a heated slice of apple.
